Description: V2-alpha Studio system theme (GTK4 / GNOME shell / icons)
 A minimalist, premium, artist-focused monochrome theme designed for the V2-alpha
 studio distribution. Includes GTK4 styles, optional GNOME Shell CSS, icon set,
 wallpapers, and GSettings schemas for theme defaults.
